	<h1 class="title">用虚拟现实技术治疗抑郁症，这是怎么回事</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113378/small/113378.jpg?1435590009" alt="">
